  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个建议功能的流程图，核心是从两个入口开始：一个是全新的建议（NEW），另一个是系统推送的通知（NOTIFICATION）。这两个都应该能从初始状态直接到达。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "NEW",
        "NOTIFICATION"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点分叉到NEW和NOTIFICATION两条线。那用户看到NEW状态后，有哪些操作可以走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NEW"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "NEW状态有三种去向：用户可以直接标记为已查看（CHECKED），也可以点击\"稍后处理\"进入DECIDE_LATER，或者直接忽略（IGNORED）。DECIDE_LATER这个状态比较特殊，它还能自循环——用户可能多次点击\"稍后\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NEW",
        "CHECKED",
        "DECIDE_LATER",
        "IGNORED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "DECIDE_LATER自循环我记下了。那从DECIDE_LATER出去的话，除了回到自己，还能到CHECKED和IGNORED对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DECIDE_LATER",
        "CHECKED",
        "IGNORED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DECIDE_LATER最终要么被处理掉，要么被忽略。另外NOTIFICATION那条线也要能到IGNORED和CHECKED，和NEW类似。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NOTIFICATION",
        "IGNORED",
        "CHECKED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画一下。标题定为\"Suggestions state diagram\"，用stateDiagram-v2语法。起点分叉到NEW和NOTIFICATION，NEW通过\"click on 'later'\"到DECIDE_LATER，通过\"click on 'check'\"到CHECKED，也能直接到IGNORED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "[*]",
        "NEW",
        "NOTIFICATION",
        "DECIDE_LATER",
        "CHECKED",
        "IGNORED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，NEW到IGNORED这条线我之前提过，但刚才确认需求时发现其实不需要直接忽略NEW，应该只能从DECIDE_LATER或NOTIFICATION到IGNORED。NEW只能走\"稍后\"或\"查看\"两条路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NEW",
        "IGNORED"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，我移除NEW到IGNORED的直接连线。现在结构是：起点→NEW/NOTIFICATION，NEW→DECIDE_LATER/CHECKED，NOTIFICATION→IGNORED/CHECKED，DECIDE_LATER自循环且能到IGNORED/CHECKED。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "NEW",
        "NOTIFICATION",
        "DECIDE_LATER",
        "CHECKED",
        "IGNORED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确，就是这个逻辑。",
